 previous surveys, we do not find that the\nshells in our sample are preferentially aligned relative to the Galactic plane.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2015 17:06:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2016 16:42:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-30"}
