 analyzed and\nshows how, for the supersymmetric flow, the M2-brane supersymmetry in the UV is\npolarized entirely into M5-brane supersymmetry in the infra-red.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2015 20:28:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Sep 2015 18:46:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-20"}
