 overshoot modeling approximations on\nclaims that carbon burning quenches an appreciable distance from the center of\nthe carbon core.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2015 00:35:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-15"}
