lly design.\nFinally, we experimentally validate these computational designs by fabricating\ndevices and comparing predictions with the results from confocal microscopy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2015 03:19:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2015 00:28:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 27 Jul 2016 01:12:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-28"}
