ree-free emission from a stellar or disk wind. Overall our data support\nthe picture of at least one, but probably several, giant planets orbiting\nHD100546 within 25 AU.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2015 07:31:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-02"}
